(prmwqmw nwl myl hoieAW) swry sMswr ivc hI mnu`K vwsqy AnMd hI AnMd huMdw hY[
(ies au~dm nwl) mn dI Btkxw dUr ho jwNdI hY; auh prmwqmw iml pYndw hY,
jo inrw nUr hI nUr hY, jo swry jgq dw Aslw hY, ijs vrgw hor koeI nhIN hY,
ijs ivc ivkwrwn dI koeI BI mYl nhIN hY, nwh aus ivc AigAWqw dw hnyrw hY Aqy nwh hI iqRSnw Awidk ivkwrwn dI A~g hY ]11]
(jdon mnu`K dw mn ivkwrwn vlon ht ky) ie`k prmwqmw (dI Xwd) vl jwndw hY,
qdon auh muV jnm-mrn dy kStwn ivc nhIN Awaundw[
aus dy AMdr TMF pY jwNdI hY Aqy aus dw Awpw piv`qr ho jwndw hY[
jo prmwqmw ikqy dUr d`isAw jwndw sI auh aus nUM nyVy (Awpxy AMdr hI) l`B pYndw hY ]12]
(ijs mnu`K dw mn isr& "eyk ids DwvY", jo mnu`K isr& ie`k pRBU dI Xwd ivc juVdw hY, aus dy AMdr, mwno) bwrHW sUrj cVH pYndy hn (Bwv, aus dy AMdr pUrn igAW dw pRkwS ho jwndw hY[)
aus dy AMdr (mwno) idn rwq ie`k-rs vwjy v`jdy hn[
aus nUM iqMnwn Bvnwn dy mwlk-pRBU dw dIdwr ho jwndw hY;
iek Acrj Kyf bx jwNdI hY ik auh mnu`K sDwrn bMdy qoN kilAwx-srUp prmwqmw dw rUp ho jwndw hY ]13]
(ijs mnu`K dw mn kyvl "eyk ids DwvY") auh AgMm prmwqmw dI is&iq-swlwh krdw hY,
(ies is&iq-swlwh dI brkq nwl) auh swry sMswr ivc aus pRBU nUM iek-smwn pCwxdw hY (vyKdw hY)[
nwh aus nUM koeI nIvwn id`sdw hY, nwh au~cw; iksy vlon Awdr hovy jwn inrwdrI, aus leI ie`ko ijhy hn,
ikaunik aus nUM swry jIvwn ivc prmwqmw hI ivAwpk id`sdw hY ]14]
(hy BweI!) pRBU jI swrI isRStI ivc isRStI dy-
z`ry z`ry ivc v`s rhy hn[
(ieh XkIn ilAw ky ik auh pRBU quhwfy AMdr v`s irhw hY qy sB jIvwn ivc v`s irhw hY) dUijAW dI syvw dI Aqy jo kuJ pRBU ny quhwnUM id`qw hY, aus ivc rwzI rihx dI surq pkwau[
aus dI is&iq-swlwh dIAW g`lwn kro, qw ik aus dy ies shI srUp dI sUJ bxI rhy ]15]
ijvyn pUrnmwSI nUM AkwS ivc pUrw cMd cVHdw hY qy cMd dIAW swrIAW hI klwn prgt huMdIAW hn,
iqvyn qyry AMdr BI sihj AvsQw dw prkwS hovygw,
jy SurU qoN A^Ir qk qy ivckwrly smy ivc (Bwv, sdw hI) mOjUd rihx vwly prmwqmw-
aus suKW dy smuMdr-pRBU ivc, hy kbIr! jy qUM cu`BI lw ky aus dw ismrn kryn ]16]
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
rwg gauVI iv`c Bgq kbIr jI dI bwxI 'vwr'[
mYn hr vyly prmwqmw dy gux gwaundw hwn (Bwv, pRBU dI is&iq-swlwh pRBU nUM imlx dw shI qrIkw hY)
gurU dy crnwn ivc A~pV ky mYn ieh Byq l`B ilAw hY ijs nwl prmwqmw nUM iml skIdw hY ]1] rhwau ]
('bwr bwr hir ky gun' gw ky, jo mnu`K) prmwqmw dI BgqI SurU krdw hY,
ieh BgqI aus dy srIr-Gr nUM QMmHI dw kMm dyndI hY,
aus dy mn dy PurinAW nUM shwrw dyndI hY (Bwv, aus dy igAW-ieMdRy Aqy mn dy Purny Btkxon ht jwndy hn)[ BgqI nwl sugMDq hoeI aus dI surq idn rwq lgwqwr (pRBU-crnwn ivc) juVI rihMdI hY[
qdon Afolqw ivc itkx krky mn dy AMdr (mwno) ie`k-rs bMsrI v`jdI hY ]1]
('bwr bwr hir ky gun' gwvx nwl mnu`K dy mn ivc) SwnqI TMF dw AMm੍irq vrHdw hY,
(ieh AMm੍irq) c`Kx nwl mn qurq swry ivkwr dUr kr dyndw hY,
siqgurU dI bwxI dI brkq nwl (mnu`K dw ivkwrwn vlon) roikAw hoieAw mn pRBU dy dr qy itikAw rihMdw hY
Aqy msq hoieAw mn aus AMm੍irq nUM pIndw rihMdw hY ]2]
('bwr bwr hir ky gun' gw ky) mnu`K Awpxy mn dy duAwly is&iq-swlwh dw, mwno, iklHw bxw lYNdw hY,
kwmwidk pMj corwn dw (h`lw krn dw) FMg smJ lYNdw hY (ies qrHW auhnwn dw vwr hox nhIN dyndw)[
(hy BweI!) qUM BI (AYsy) iklHy nUM C`f ky bwhr nwh jweIn (Bwv, Awpxy mn nUM bwhr Btkx n dyeIn),
nhIN qW ieh mn (ivkwrwn ivc pY ky) bVw duKI hovygw ]3]
('bwr bwr hir ky gun' gw ky, mnu`K AwpxI) sUJ ivc pRBU dy nwm dw cwnx pYdw kr lYNdw hY,
ihrdy-kml ivc prmwqmw dw invws bxw lYNdw hY;
siqgurU nUM iml ky Awqmw qy prmwqmw dI swnJ bxw dyndw hY,
(pihlwn mwieAw vl) prqy mn nUM v`s ivc kr ky pRBU dy snmuK kr dyndw hY ]4]
('bwr bwr hir ky gun' gw ky, mnu`K) mwieAw (dy pRBwv) nUM (is&iq-swlwh dy pRvwh ivc) roVH dyndw hY,
mwieAw dy iqMny hI (blI) guxwn nUM ie`k pRBU (dI Xwd) ivc lIn kr dyndw hY[
(jo lok is&iq-swlwh C`f ky mwieAw dI) iK`J ivc rihMdy hn, auh mwieAw dIAW q੍ir-guxI ndIAW ivc hI (goqy KWdy) hn,
idn rwq mMd-krm (krdy hn, is&iq-swlwh qoN vwnjy rihx krky auhnwn nUM) Dondy nhIN hn ]5]
