Aqy ies AOKI GwtI au~qy cVHdw hY ik hr vyly Awpxy Awp nwl lVweI krdw hY (Bwv, Awpxy mn nUM muV muV ivkwrwn vlon rokdw hY),
pMjwn hI igAW-ieMd੍irAW nUM v`s ivc r`Kdw hY,
qdon (iksy au~qy BI) kdy aus dI myr-qyr dI ingwh nhIN pYndI ]6]
